videos.description: After being benched for the start of Oklahoma's game against Baylor, Kyler Murray returns and finds Lee Morris for a 9-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Murray returns from benching to throw 9-yard TD

videos.description: Kyler Murray throws to Grant Calcaterra who makes an incredible leaping catch to complete a 30-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Oklahoma WR makes amazing leaping catch for 30-yard TD

videos.description: Charlie Brewer gets Baylor on the board as he throws to Denzel  Mims for a 13-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Baylor's Brewer finds WR for 13-yard TD

videos.description: Kyle  Murray finds Lee Morris wide open for a 43-yard touchdown as Oklahoma increases its lead over Baylor.
videos.headline: Murray completes 43-yard TD to extend Sooners' lead

videos.description: Marquise Brown eludes defenders to walk in for 24-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Sooners' Brown gallops in for 24-yard TD

videos.description: Kyler Murray throws to CeeDee Lamb, who goes in for  an 86-yard touchdown as the Sooners extend their lead over Baylor.
videos.headline: Murray throws 5th TD pass vs. Baylor

videos.description: Baylors' Charlie Brewer rushes in for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Baylor QB powers in for 1-yard TD

videos.description: Kyler Murray's superb outing continues as he throws to Marquise Brown for his sixth touchdown pass of the day.
videos.headline: Murray finds receiver for 6th TD pass
